translation.Name: Rio Note - Traveller #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: I can't believe it, I'm finally going back home after having to stay here for months due to work, I've finished the research months ago, yet I had to stay until the time was over! I don't get it.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: I hope that they haven't closed all the airports back in China, yet. I don't want to be stuck here.
